This Amelia model is a very affordable home for in the sought-after PGA Verano. You will smile when you come home with its charming front porch & upgraded landscaping and walk to the Talavera Clubhouse. E-Z move the furniture is negotiable! Enjoy the many upgrades, from all tile floors, all impact glass windows, upgraded light fixtures, plantations shutters and more. Cooks love this open kitchen with SS appliances, granite countertops & breakfast bar. Relax in the spacious main bedroom with 2 walk-in closets, a bath with dual vanities sinks,  soaking tub & separate shower PGA Verano is an amenity-filled luxury community that offers residents 3 nearby championship golf courses: the 54-hole PGA Golf Club, The Private Legacy Golf and Tennis Club, and the new Astor Creek Country Club. There is an enticing selection of restaurants, ranging from light meals to gourmet dining, and nearby shopping venues include mainstream consumer retail outlets, specialty boutiques, 3 excellent hospitals, and many healthcare providers. The Telavera Clubhouse is 40,000 sg ft chuck filled with amenities, including indoor and outdoor pools, a lavish gym with lush locker rooms, 5 Har-Tru Hydro Tennis Courts, 27 Pickleball Courts, a separate 7000 sg ft E-Gym with resistance pool, saunas, card room, ballrooms for planned events and so much more. It is a lot of value for a moderate HOA monthly. Call today for your exclusive tour.
